atst.giss.abplc

Class ABPlcioChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Channel
      • atst.giss.abplc.ABPlcioChannel

  • public class ABPlcioChannel
extends Channel
    This is the GISS channel class used by the ABPlcioConnection class to read and write PLC tags to the GIS PLC. Each tag has its own channel. The channel has a name that equates to the tag's name.

    On creation the channel uses atst.cs.util.Misc.getSharedObject() to obtain a reference to the ABPlcioMaster through the IABPlcioMaster interface. When requested to open, read, write and close a channel to the PLC it is done by calling the PLC access method of the ABPlcioMaster.
